body: @Raj-08 Currently tf.nn.dilation and tf.nn.erosion are not supported in TFLite per se, some of the dilation/erosion options are embedded in conv that are potentially modifiable. Alternatively, you can add a custom op as described [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/custom_operators.md) or only use the ops the are currently supported by TFLite in your model.
